Package com.pingidentity.sdk.provision.groups.request

Interface UpdateGroupRequestContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProvisioningRequestContext
    public interface UpdateGroupRequestContext
extends ProvisioningRequestContext
    An interface that represents the request context for a update group operation. It contains all the information needed to fulfill the request, e.g. group attributes.
